subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Athletics and Sports
Track and Field
Pole Vault
lead_paragraph: With an Olympics looming in Beijing, the world track and field championships that begin Saturday in Osaka, Japan, are a prologue. A look at some of the most intriguing events.
